name: Rope Necklace - Gold and Taupe
description:
Soft with a light sheen, this nautical-inspired statement necklace easily updates an outfit.  With a chocolate satin ribbon, the necklace's length is easily adjustable. Switch out the ribbon for one of your scarves for a personal, unique look!

Materials:  Cotton/Poly blend rope, Satin ribbon
Lightweight: 2.2 oz or 60 gms
